long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🏆Best tool made for people who want to export IG Post, Pictures, Photos and Videos into CSV.

A helper tool, one-click to download Post, pictures, Photos and Videos from Instagram user.

🖖  KEY FEATURES:

Export photos and videos from post.

🚗 DESCRIPTION Step by Step:

1.Enter a Instagram username
2.Click the export button

⛵️ SUPPORTED COLUMNS:

post id
isVideo
videoViewCount
likeCount
commentCount
commentsDisabled
caption
postDate
postUrl
ownerUsername
ownerProfileUrl
thumbnail
coverUrl
displayResource
resource

🔎  HOW DOES IT WORK:

Using Instagram's official API to export data.
Free user can export the first 100 records.
Pro user can export the first 10000 records. Only $9.99!

🔒  USAGE POLICY

No password required. 
All the data you export is processed locally, so no one knows what you exported.
